# DocSera-Landing — Astro project (Node-based)
#
# This repo had no .gitignore until 2026-05-19 (oversight from the original
# scaffold), which is why `git status` had been showing build outputs and
# node_modules churn as untracked noise for months. .dockerignore was the
# only exclusion list, but that only affects Docker builds — git happily
# tracked everything else.
#
# Note: a few files under .astro/, dist/, and node_modules/ are already
# tracked from before this file existed (committed by accident before
# anyone noticed the missing .gitignore). This file ONLY prevents NEW
# files in those dirs from being tracked; the previously-tracked files
# stay until someone explicitly untracks them:
#     git rm --cached -r .astro/ dist/ node_modules/.package-lock.json
#     git rm --cached -r node_modules/.vite/
# Left as a future cleanup — running git rm --cached changes git tracking
# but leaves on-disk files in place, so it's reversible if needed.

# --------------------------------------------------------------------
# Build outputs
# --------------------------------------------------------------------
dist/
.astro/

# --------------------------------------------------------------------
# Dependencies
# --------------------------------------------------------------------
node_modules/

# --------------------------------------------------------------------
# Local secrets / env
# --------------------------------------------------------------------
.env
.env.local
.env.production
.env.production.local
.env.development.local

# --------------------------------------------------------------------
# Editor / IDE
# --------------------------------------------------------------------
.vscode/
.idea/
*.iml

# --------------------------------------------------------------------
# OS
# --------------------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# --------------------------------------------------------------------
# Logs
# --------------------------------------------------------------------
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# --------------------------------------------------------------------
# Caches
# --------------------------------------------------------------------
.vite/
.cache/
.parcel-cache/
